{"tid":1112583,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【安心偷食】台灣占星專家批年底前有答案 Selina：婚姻是2個人的事","createTime":"2019-04-17T12:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T14:33:12.000Z","uid":225846,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"99f300a7350fa59c345fdde2df397cd4dbe71fb1","tid":1112583,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T12:51:20.000Z","msg":"許志安與黃心穎車廂偷食，震驚的不止香港，連鄰近的兩岸都的fans都大感震驚，其中大陸網民昨日在許志安的微博中洗版，以逾8,000條留言鬧爆他，有人叫他離開鄭秀文（Sammi），甚至有人覺得童話破滅（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2DcpWD5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2DcpWD5&d=BZ3h%2BuUaIL2OU9i9OZdAr8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=069b9f7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2DcpWD5</a> ）。<br />\n<br />\n而台灣傳媒亦大肆報道「安心偷食」，其中組合S.H.E的任家萱（Selina）今天錄影節目時被問到此事，她說早已有心理準備會被問，曾經有過一段婚姻的她坦言：「婚姻是2個人的事，外人不方便多說甚麼。」<br />\n<br />\n至於同場還有台灣西洋占星學專家唐綺陽擔任嘉賓，唐綺陽認為今次許志安和Sammi爆出婚變，並不一定是壞事，更指分開對兩人來說可能是好事，因為讓他們直接面對問題。唐綺陽更認為Sammi一直瘦下去不是辦法，讓他們趁此機會把感受講出來也是好事。<br />\n<br />\n唐綺陽指許志安和Sammi同屬獅子座，她評析獅子座今年因木星逆行關係，感情舊賬可能紛紛出籠，唐綺陽指木星逆行大概4個月，<span style=\"color: red;\">預計許志安和Sammi可以趁此段時間處理問題，年底前就會有答案。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔講真係唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c8e49afa5fef1c2708986893434feff86dfab3","tid":1112583,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T12:55:47.000Z","msg":"星座撚有事即刻賴相剋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146a3072b7454f37358ad3492fdf58f05af00fb4","tid":1112583,"uid":189911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T14:33:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bCGO1Nn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbCGO1Nn.jpg&h=6d013275&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}